Available Tools: create_deal | update_deal_stage | get_deal | list_deals_by_stage | close_deal
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "deal_id": "string", "contact_id": "string", "stage": "string", "value": number }
Response Schema: { "deal_id": "string", "name": "string", "stage": "string", "value": number, "probability": number }
---
Question: Create a new deal for Acme Corp with contact ID C-1024 in the prospect stage valued at 15000.
Call: { "func_call": "create_deal", "deal_id": "D-8821", "contact_id": "C-1024", "stage": "prospect", "value": 15000 }
Response: { "deal_id": "D-8821", "name": "Acme Corp Expansion", "stage": "prospect", "value": 15000, "probability": 10 }

